\frametitle{Command Line Interface (CLI)}
I developed a CLI to bridge the gap between cluster management and quantum job submission.
\begin{exampleblock}{Sample Usage}
\begin{verbatim}
$ ./q-hpc-cli --simulate --qubits 5 --depth 20
$ ./q-hpc-cli --submit-cluster --node-count 4
\end{verbatim}
\end{exampleblock}
This allows for automated batching of quantum circuits across a classical cluster.
